[
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">Listen</st> to <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>, O <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">family</st> of <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">you who are <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">called</st> by the <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">name</st> \u201c<st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>,\u201d<p class=\"poetry\">and are <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">descended</st> <st data-num=\"04578\">from</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">who <st data-num=\"07650\" class=\"\">take oaths</st> in the <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">name</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"02142\" class=\"\">invoke</st><n id=\"3\" /> the <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">but <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> in an <st data-num=\"0571\" class=\"\">honest</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"06666\" class=\"\">just</st> <st data-num=\"0571 06666\">manner</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Indeed</st>, they <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">live</st> in the <st data-num=\"06944\" class=\"\">holy</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"05564\" class=\"\">trust</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">in</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">whose <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">name</st> is the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">announced</st> <st data-num=\"07223\" class=\"\">events</st> <st data-num=\"0227\" class=\"\">beforehand</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">issued</st> the <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">decrees</st> and <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">made</st> the <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">predictions</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06597\" class=\"\">suddenly</st> I <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">acted</st> and they <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came to pass</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I did this<n id=\"1\" /> because I <st data-num=\"01847\" class=\"\">know</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">how</st> <st data-num=\"07186\" class=\"\">stubborn</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> are.<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"06203\" class=\"\">neck</st> <st data-num=\"01517\" class=\"\">muscles</st> are like <st data-num=\"01270\" class=\"\">iron</st><p class=\"poetry\">and your <st data-num=\"04696\" class=\"\">forehead</st> like <st data-num=\"05154\" class=\"\">bronze</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">announced</st> them to you <st data-num=\"0227\" class=\"\">beforehand</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02962\" class=\"\">before</st> they <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">happened</st>, I <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">predicted</st> them for you,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06435\" class=\"\">so</st> you could <st data-num=\"06435\" class=\"\">never</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018My <st data-num=\"06091\" class=\"\">image</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">did</st> these things,<p class=\"poetry\">my <st data-num=\"06459\" class=\"\">idol</st>, my <st data-num=\"05262\" class=\"\">cast image</st>, <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">decreed</st> them.\u2019</p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">You have <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard;</st> now <st data-num=\"02372\" class=\"\">look at</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the evidence!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Will <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">admit</st> that what I say is true?<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">From <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">this point on</st> I am <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">announcing</st> to you <st data-num=\"02319\" class=\"\">new events</st><p class=\"poetry\">that are previously <st data-num=\"05341\" class=\"\">unrevealed</st> and you do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know about</st>.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Now</st> they <st data-num=\"01254\" class=\"\">come into being</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0227\" class=\"\">in the past</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">today</st> you did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">hear about</st> them,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06435\" class=\"\">so</st> you could <st data-num=\"06435\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Yes</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> I <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know about</st> them.\u2019</p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">You did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">hear</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">you do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">you were <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06605 0241\">told</st> <st data-num=\"0227\" class=\"\">beforehand</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> I <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> that you <st data-num=\"0898\" class=\"\">are</st> <st data-num=\"0901\" class=\"\">very</st> <st data-num=\"0898\" class=\"\">deceitful</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">you were <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">labeled</st><n id=\"3\" /> a <st data-num=\"06586\" class=\"\">rebel</st> from <st data-num=\"0990\" class=\"\">birth</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04616\" class=\"\">For the sake of</st> my <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">reputation</st><n id=\"1\" /> I <st data-num=\"0748\" class=\"\">hold back</st> my <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">for the sake of my <st data-num=\"08416\" class=\"\">prestige</st><n id=\"2\" /> I <st data-num=\"02413\" class=\"\">restrain</st> myself <st data-num=\"01115\" class=\"\">from</st> <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">destroying</st> you.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>, I have <st data-num=\"06884\" class=\"\">refined</st> you, but <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> as <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">I have <st data-num=\"0974\" class=\"\">purified</st> you<n id=\"1\" /> in the <st data-num=\"03564\" class=\"\">furnace</st> of <st data-num=\"06040\" class=\"\">misery</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04616\" class=\"\">For</st> my <st data-num=\"04616\" class=\"\">sake</st> <st data-num=\"04616\" class=\"\">alone</st><n id=\"1\" /> I will <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">act</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"0349\" class=\"\">how</st> can I allow my name to be <st data-num=\"02490\" class=\"\">defiled</st>?<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">share</st> my <st data-num=\"03519\" class=\"\">glory</st> with <st data-num=\"0312\" class=\"\">anyone else</st>!<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">Listen</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me, O <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, whom I <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">summoned</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">the one</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am <st data-num=\"07223\" class=\"\">present at the very beginning</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0637\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"0314\" class=\"\">at the very end</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0637\" class=\"\">Yes</st>, my <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> <st data-num=\"03245\" class=\"\">founded</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">my <st data-num=\"03225\" class=\"\">right hand</st> <st data-num=\"02946\" class=\"\">spread out</st> the <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">sky</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"07121 0413\">summon</st> them;<p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">stand</st> <st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">together</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> of you, <st data-num=\"06908\" class=\"\">gather together</st> and <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">listen</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> among them<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">announced</st> <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">these things</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"0157\" class=\"\">ally</st><n id=\"2\" /> will <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">carry out</st> his <st data-num=\"02656\" class=\"\">desire</st> against <st data-num=\"0894\" class=\"\">Babylon</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">he will exert his <st data-num=\"02220\" class=\"\">power</st> against the <st data-num=\"03778\" class=\"\">Babylonians</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st>, <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> have <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">spoken</st>\u2014<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0637\" class=\"\">yes</st>, I have <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">summoned</st> him;<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">lead</st> him and he will <st data-num=\"06743 01870\">succeed</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07126 0413\">Approach</st> me\u2014<st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">listen</st> to <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">From the very <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">first</st> I have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">spoken</st> in <st data-num=\"05643\" class=\"\">secret</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">when</st> it <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">happens</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st>.\u201d<p class=\"poetry\">So <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st>, the <st data-num=\"0136\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> me, accompanied by his <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">Spirit</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, your <st data-num=\"01350\" class=\"\">Protector</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"06918\" class=\"\">Holy One</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>:<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">who <st data-num=\"03925\" class=\"\">teaches</st> you how to <st data-num=\"03276\" class=\"\">succeed</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">who <st data-num=\"01869\" class=\"\">leads</st> you in the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">way</st> you should <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">go</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03863\" class=\"\">If only</st> you had <st data-num=\"07181\" class=\"\">obeyed</st> my<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"04687\" class=\"\">commandments</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">prosperity</st> would have <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">flowed</st> to you like a <st data-num=\"05104\" class=\"\">river</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06666\" class=\"\">deliverance</st> would have come to you like the <st data-num=\"01530\" class=\"\">waves</st> of the <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">sea</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"02233\" class=\"\">descendants</st> would have <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">been</st> as numerous as <st data-num=\"02344\" class=\"\">sand</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"04578\" class=\"\">your</st> <st data-num=\"06631\" class=\"\">children</st><n id=\"2\" /> like its <st data-num=\"04579\" class=\"\">granules</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">name</st> would <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> have been <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">cut off</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"08045\" class=\"\">eliminated</st> from my <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">presence</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">Leave</st> <st data-num=\"0894\" class=\"\">Babylon</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01272\" class=\"\">Flee</st> from the <st data-num=\"03778\" class=\"\">Babylonians</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">Announce</st> it with a <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">shout</st> of <st data-num=\"07440\" class=\"\">joy</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">Make</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">known</st>\u2014<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">proclaim</st> it <st data-num=\"05704 07097\">throughout</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">Say</st>, \u2018The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01350\" class=\"\">protects</st><n id=\"2\" /> his <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st> <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06770\" class=\"\">thirst</st> as he <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">leads</st> them through <st data-num=\"02723\" class=\"\">dry regions</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">he makes <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st> <st data-num=\"05140\" class=\"\">flow out</st> of a <st data-num=\"06697\" class=\"\">rock</st> for them;<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"01234\" class=\"\">splits open</st> a <st data-num=\"06697\" class=\"\">rock</st> and <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st> <st data-num=\"02100\" class=\"\">flows out</st>.\u2019<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "48",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">There will be no</st> <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">prosperity</st> for the <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">wicked</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  }
]